## Verification Plan

### Automated
- `pip install fastapi uvicorn matplotlib numpy` then `python3 main.py`
- Open `http://localhost:8000` in browser
- Click "Run" with default config and verify results + charts appear

### Manual
- Verify optimal plan prioritizes critical devices (Ventilator)
- Verify all 5 visualizations render correctly
- Test with modified parameters to see different optimal plans
